===========================================================================
jQuery Touch And Drop
Brian Notess, http://briannotess.com/, @bnotess
============================================================================

ABOUT

jQuery Touch And Drop is a simple, lightweight plugin for adding drag and drop functionality to touch screen web applications. 
-------------------------------------------

OPTION PARAMETERS

onDrop        function
Write a function to be executed when each element is "dropped" (touched).
Defaults, null

minMove      number
Choose a minimum number of pixels an element has to move before the callback is executed
Defaults to 20.


-------------------------------------------

EXAMPLES

Add drag and drop functionality to elements with the class attribute 'touchme'. If the element is moved more than 15 pixels in any direction, a function will run adding '<p> Dropped! </p>' to a div element with the id "alerts".

  $(document).ready(function(){
		
	$('.touchme').touchAndDrop({
		onDrop: function() {$('#alerts').html('<p> Dropped! </p>')},
		minMove: 15
	});
});	


